比10至20個朋友,記得今晚10點開始Facebook 集體檢舉!"},{"pid":"d50ce84e6dcd94ea8fa11eaaa6a965ac55e9c154","tid":1445057,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWQ8WpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWQ8WpL.jpg&h=afa56da5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n極度懷疑政府口口聲聲講嘅暴力全部都係警察所為"},{"pid":"3339e39813c5251596e18f9fb2bee4219417d439","tid":1445057,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"d7cb780a7200878f86e7ec7bcf831427deb490e5","tid":1445057,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3339e39813c5251596e18f9fb2bee4219417d439","tid":1445057,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"56de2589297816818a707a73923338a8ae308d5c","tid":1445057,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de859114de8b606ff4330c9c0a9b4f7c377adf4b","tid":1445057,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"3a24f54796e5b913074a18629e13bf42413558db","tid":1445057,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a884fc5bfc18b68087a069b43cbabc7c6674a73c","tid":1445057,"uid":37464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84468977093e5ea2a145b6252aabc31008cfeb3a","tid":1445057,"uid":128190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-1